The paper deals with medical image classification, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves Multiple Task Learning (MTL), which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of existing data to improve classification performance, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques, such as rephrasing the classification problem, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of information extraction from data, which is a common theme in information retrieval (cs.IR).
